ont-medium cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between gap-2\">Is Number of Integers With Popcount-Depth Equal to K II good for interviews?<span class=\"text-muted-foreground group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform\">+</span></summary><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Yes — as a Hard problem it is a solid practice target. Pair it with related problems in the same pattern family for spaced repetition.</p></details><details class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-4 group\"><summary class=\"font-medium cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between gap-2\">Where can I read the official statement?<span class=\"text-muted-foreground group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform\">+</span></summary><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Open the official LeetCode page for constraints and examples: https://leetcode.com/problems/number-of-integers-with-popcount-depth-equal-to-k-ii/</p></details></div></section><section id=\"related\" class=\"mt-12 scroll-mt-24\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-3\">Related problems</h2><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm\"><thead class=\"bg-muted/60 text-left\"><tr><th class=\"px-3 py-2.5 font-semibold w-16\">#</th><th class=\"px-3 py-2.5 font-semibold\">Title</th><th class=\"px-3 py-2.5 font-semibold hidden sm:table-cell\">Difficulty</th><th class=\"px-3 py-2.5 font-semibold hidden md:table-cell\">Topics</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-t border-border hover:bg-muted/40\"><td class=\"px-3 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground tabular-nums\">3671</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2.5\"><a class=\"font-medium hover:text-primary\" href=\"/problems/sum-of-beautiful-subsequences\">Sum of Beautiful Subsequences</a></td><td class=\"px-3 py-2.5 hidden sm:table-cell\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide bg-hard/15 text-hard\">Hard</span></td><td class=\"px-3 py-2.5 hidden md:table-cell text-muted-foregrou